1
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:29,950
[The Story of Xing Fu]

2
00:01:30,050 --> 00:01:32,950
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,000
Chicken.

4
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:01,719
Where's the chicken?

5
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:13,520
There you are.

6
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,039
Yani!

7
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:27,400
Goodness.

8
00:02:28,319 --> 00:02:28,840
Get back here.

9
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,120
Get over here.

10
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:43,759
Yani.

11
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,599
Aren't you on a business trip?

12
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:48,240
It's okay.

13
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,319
Don't be scared.

14
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,120
Okay.

15
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,120
I'll put it away.

16
00:02:53,759 --> 00:02:55,159
Didn't Qinglai and Xingfu

17
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,479
already move out?

18
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:58,039
Move out?

19
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,960
Why?

20
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:06,639
Anyway...

21
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,800
Did you buy this for Qingzhi's birthday?

22
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,000
It must be expensive.

23
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,159
Ms. Lin.

24
00:03:18,719 --> 00:03:20,479
Did you take the towel from the bathroom?

25
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:21,919
Yes.

26
00:03:23,439 --> 00:03:24,280
Yes, I did.

27
00:03:24,599 --> 00:03:25,520
This is to wipe the toilet bowl.

28
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,719
Put it back.

29
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,439
You need to wipe the toilet bowl?

30
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:30,240
It's pretty clean.

31
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,759
Look, it's clean.

32
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,599
It's no problem.

33
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:37,039
Ms. Lin, tell Qingzhi

34
00:03:37,039 --> 00:03:38,080
that I dropped by.

35
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:39,599
I have something to do.

36
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:41,039
I'll leave first.

37
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,520
Yani...

38
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:45,080
Oh.

39
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,840
Look at me.

40
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:48,599
Well...

41
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:51,319
I could tell.

42
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:53,960
Is it an inconvenience for you
that his brother and sister-in-law

43
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,199
are staying here?

44
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,439
You don't like it, right?

45
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,840
Not at all.

46
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,159
Qingzhi owns this house.

47
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,560
Who he invites here

48
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,639
is not up to me.

49
00:04:04,919 --> 00:04:06,039
Listen to you.

50
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,199
But it's true.

51
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:10,319
Qingzhi owns this house.

52
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,560
To be frank,

53
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,319
the whole family

54
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:13,039
had to fork out our savings

55
00:04:13,039 --> 00:04:14,240
to help him buy the house.

56
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,520
Where else would he find the money?

57
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,879
I know, Ms. Lin.

58
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,439
Good that you do, Yani.

59
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:22,839
Qingzhi made it clear to us.

60
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:25,040
That the two of you are truly in love.

61
00:04:25,800 --> 00:04:26,720
Then tell me,

62
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,399
you've chosen him

63
00:04:28,399 --> 00:04:29,519
and he's marrying you.

64
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:31,079
Aren't we one family then?

65
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:33,120
In a family,

66
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,759
when one of us

67
00:04:33,839 --> 00:04:34,800
is in trouble,

68
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:35,879
the rest

69
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,480
should come out and help.

70
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,279
No?

71
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,920
I get it, Ms. Lin.

72
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:46,000
Then...

73
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,600
I have something to do.

74
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,759
I have to go.

75
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,439
No, no.

76
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,199
Stay and eat.

77
00:04:50,279 --> 00:04:51,160
I'm about to cook.

78
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:51,519
See?

79
00:04:51,519 --> 00:04:52,839
It's fine. I have an urgent matter.

80
00:04:52,959 --> 00:04:54,240
I'll treat you to a meal next time, Ms. Lin.

81
00:04:54,279 --> 00:04:55,399
What is so urgent?

82
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,560
I'm off, Ms. Lin.

83
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,199
Bye.

84
00:04:57,199 --> 00:04:58,720
When will you come and eat?

85
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:09,360
Yani.

86
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,519
Wang Qingzhi.

87
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,000
Didn't you say your brother and sister-in-law

88
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,160
have moved out?

89
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,399
Yes, they have.

90
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:18,040
You liar!

91
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,199
I just left the house.

92
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:21,759
It's a mess!

93
00:05:23,279 --> 00:05:24,360
You're back?

94
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:26,079
Aren't you supposed to be away for a week?

95
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,639
So you lied to me?

96
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,600
I wanted to come back earlier

97
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,639
to surprise you.

98
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:33,600
I guess it was my own wishful thinking.

99
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:34,920
Right now,

100
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,399
you're not showing me any respect.

101
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:37,720
One more thing.

102
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:38,720
I'm done with the house.

103
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:40,160
Wait, Yani. Let me explain.

104
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:54,519
(Hello. The number you've dialed is unavailable.)

105
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:57,079
(Please try again later.)

106
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:34,959
Mom.

107
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:36,800
Hey.

108
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:38,480
I came home as soon as I got your call.

109
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:39,600
You're back.

110
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,480
Where is Little Dou?

111
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,439
He's outside.

112
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:43,480
His grandpa took him down to play.

113
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:43,959
I see.

114
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,480
Take this.

115
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:05,959
Dad.

116
00:07:06,759 --> 00:07:07,240
Xingfu.

117
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,360
Little Dou, let me hold him.

118
00:07:10,079 --> 00:07:10,959
-He sleeps soundly.
-How is he?

119
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,160
He's grown, right?

120
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:14,079
Yes, he looks different.

121
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,480
My Little Dou.

122
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:40,879
What's the matter?

123
00:07:41,199 --> 00:07:41,839
What's with you?

124
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,279
Why are you back today?

125
00:07:43,959 --> 00:07:45,399
You said it was for a week, right?

126
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:47,360
Today is Qingzhi's birthday.

127
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,360
I came back earlier

128
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,160
hoping to surprise him.

129
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,120
So why did you come home?

130
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,839
We had a fight.

131
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,199
Talk to me.

132
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,839
What did he do?

133
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:00,720
Tell me he's being an idiot.

134
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:02,360
The whole time I was away,

135
00:08:02,519 --> 00:08:03,279
he kept telling me

136
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,639
that Qinglai and Xingfu had moved out.

137
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,879
Why did he lie to me?

138
00:08:06,439 --> 00:08:07,360
Just tell me they didn't move out.

139
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,560
Today, his parents came too.

140
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,959
The moment I opened the door today,

141
00:08:09,959 --> 00:08:11,519
the house was practically inhabitable.

142
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,160
It was reeking of cigarette smoke.

143
00:08:13,759 --> 00:08:15,040
They were going to slaughter a chicken inside.

144
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:16,560
One by one.

145
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,240
Listen.

146
00:08:17,759 --> 00:08:18,439
Back then,

147
00:08:18,439 --> 00:08:19,600
when your uncles from the countryside

148
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,560
came to our house,

149
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:21,839
they threw their dirty socks

150
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:23,279
onto the sofa.

151
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,360
They were smoking

152
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:26,560
and almost burned the house down.

153
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,079
You're exaggerating.

154
00:08:28,079 --> 00:08:28,600
It's true.

155
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,399
Only you

156
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,560
will get irritated easily.

157
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:31,800
-Who said so?
-Yani.

158
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,879
I'm telling the truth.

159
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,519
Perhaps he lied

160
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:36,039
for a reason, right?

161
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,399
It could be a white lie.

162
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,519
That's acceptable.

163
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,679
So why did he lie?

164
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,240
It's about his character.

165
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:41,879
Understand?

166
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:42,679
You...

167
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:44,679
There's something more ridiculous.

168
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,440
When I went to the house,

169
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:48,279
his mother gave me a whole lecture
about how their family

170
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:49,519
went through so much.

171
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:51,360
She said Qingzhi was the one who bought the house.

172
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,559
If we're going to be family,

173
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:53,759
we should do this and that.

174
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:54,519
She kept lecturing me.

175
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,120
Like I said, it's the same.

176
00:08:56,320 --> 00:08:57,360
Back then, your grandma

177
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,559
also preached the same thing.

178
00:08:59,279 --> 00:09:00,600
Before she passed away, she grabbed my hand

179
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,279
and held it tight.

180
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,000
She insisted that I look after your uncles

181
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:04,240
and all their kids.

182
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:06,279
Her grandma...

183
00:09:06,480 --> 00:09:07,799
She died so many years ago.

184
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,720
Are you still bringing that up now?

185
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:10,919
Yes, I am.

186
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:12,879
I will forever remember it.

187
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,120
I felt so wronged

188
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,639
marrying you back then.

189
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,639
Listen up.

190
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:18,799
I'm not letting Yani make the same mistake.

191
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:19,840
Yani, listen to me.

192
00:09:20,399 --> 00:09:21,879
You must not make the same mistake.

193
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,440
If you make the wrong choice,

194
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:25,240
you'll regret it for the rest of your life.

195
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,879
The girl is already upset.

196
00:09:26,879 --> 00:09:28,639
Why must you make things worse?

197
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,000
Making things worse?

198
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,360
I'm just telling Yani

199
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,480
about my grievances

200
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,799
and what I went through back then.

201
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:35,759
Yani, listen.

202
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,039
Do you know what happened to me?

203
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,519
When I was pregnant with you,

204
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,679
your dad was away for business.

205
00:09:39,799 --> 00:09:41,720
I didn't have any warm meals.

206
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:43,440
Your dad shirked his responsibility

207
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,759
and got your grandma to come

208
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,759
and take care of me.

209
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:46,639
In the end,

210
00:09:46,639 --> 00:09:47,840
do you know what happened?

211
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:48,919
Not only

212
00:09:48,919 --> 00:09:50,200
did your grandma come,

213
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,679
but she also brought along

214
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:53,720
all your uncles.

215
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:54,559
Who understands

216
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,679
my suffering?

217
00:09:55,919 --> 00:09:56,799
Was it easy for me?

218
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:57,639
Also,

219
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,600
your second uncle was working
in another province,

220
00:09:59,639 --> 00:10:01,679
and he wanted me to get him a transfer.

221
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:02,679
Now, you go and choose

222
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:03,600
a guy like Qingzhi.

223
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:04,200
Tell me.

224
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:04,679
A guy like Qingzhi.

225
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:06,000
How do you expect me to be okay with it?

226
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,120
I can't accept it.

227
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,039
His age...

228
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:11,480
What are you doing?

229
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,639
Where are you going?

230
00:10:16,159 --> 00:10:17,200
I'm fine now, Mom.

231
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:19,360
I'm going to get changed.

232
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,759
Goodness.

233
00:10:29,639 --> 00:10:30,080
Baby.

234
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,799
Are you just going to stare at your son?

235
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:36,039
It's time to eat.

236
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:38,120
I haven't seen him for so long.

237
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,200
I miss him.

238
00:10:40,200 --> 00:10:41,679
I want to be with him a little longer.

239
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,200
If you can't bear to leave him,

240
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,960
then go back with us.

241
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,200
Go back?

242
00:10:50,799 --> 00:10:51,480
We came here

243
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,840
to talk to you about this.

244
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:58,080
Baby, let your mother eat.

245
00:10:58,639 --> 00:11:00,519
He's a good kid just like Qinglai.

246
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:02,919
Go eat. Food's getting cold.

247
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:03,840
Let's go.

248
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,759
Go and eat.

249
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:08,879
Come on.

250
00:11:12,039 --> 00:11:12,720
Nice, right?

251
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:15,279
Mr. Wan visited the family

252
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:16,000
and brought gifts.

253
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,919
It's this chicken.

254
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:18,320
Your dad and I brought it here.

255
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,639
Come on, dig in.

256
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:23,320
Drinking in a place like this,

257
00:11:23,519 --> 00:11:24,279
even the wine tastes better.

258
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,720
Qinglai, come on.

259
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,320
Qingzhi.

260
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,039
Come on, let's drink.

261
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,879
Qingzhi.

262
00:11:30,879 --> 00:11:32,879
We've been busy looking for a house.

263
00:11:33,159 --> 00:11:34,720
We forgot it's your birthday.

264
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:35,679
Allow me to offer a toast

265
00:11:35,679 --> 00:11:36,879
and wish you a happy birthday.

266
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:37,879
Thanks, Xingfu.

267
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,080
Don't thank me.

268
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:40,159
Your brother and I

269
00:11:40,159 --> 00:11:41,759
have caused you and Yani enough trouble.

270
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,200
We should thank you instead.

271
00:11:43,679 --> 00:11:44,480
But don't worry.

272
00:11:44,559 --> 00:11:46,039
We'll move out very soon.

273
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,360
Qingzhi.

274
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,639
Qinglai and Xingfu are staying here just fine.

275
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,639
I don't get why

276
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:05,519
they have to move out.

277
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:06,639
That's right.

278
00:12:07,519 --> 00:12:08,519
The house is spacious.

279
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,720
It's big enough to house everyone.

280
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,159
Dad, Mom.

281
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,440
Yani and Qingzhi will live here
after they get married.

282
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,519
It's not proper for us to stay here.

283
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:18,799
That's true.

284
00:12:23,759 --> 00:12:24,919
Qingzhi, Yani must have said something to you,

285
00:12:24,919 --> 00:12:25,519
didn't she?

286
00:12:27,879 --> 00:12:28,600
She didn't.

287
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:30,600
Don't lie to me.

288
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,519
I'm not dumb.

289
00:12:32,559 --> 00:12:33,799
I will be the voice of reason.

290
00:12:34,879 --> 00:12:36,840
What right does Yani have to be upset?

291
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,360
This house isn't hers.

292
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,519
It's ours.

293
00:12:41,799 --> 00:12:43,000
Your brother and sister-in-law

294
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:44,600
only came to you

295
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,879
because they're in a pickle.

296
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:47,279
Why can't they stay here?

297
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:50,240
People say, a pica pica with its long tail,

298
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,559
marries a wife and forgets the mother.

299
00:12:51,919 --> 00:12:53,000
You haven't even gotten married yet

300
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,120
and you've forgotten your family.

301
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,039
Mom.

302
00:13:02,919 --> 00:13:04,799
Yani wants to break up with me.

303
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,039
What?

304
00:13:08,919 --> 00:13:09,600
What did you say?

305
00:13:15,399 --> 00:13:16,639
Just break up then.

306
00:13:17,639 --> 00:13:18,919
It might be hard to find a three-legged toad,

307
00:13:18,919 --> 00:13:20,440
but two-legged humans are everywhere.

308
00:13:21,039 --> 00:13:22,559
A woman that doesn't get the realities of life

309
00:13:22,559 --> 00:13:24,360
will only become a burden if you marry her.

310
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:25,399
What are you saying?

311
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:26,519
-Qinglai.
-What's wrong with you?

312
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:28,120
If you're unhappy with me,

313
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,159
just say it to my face.

314
00:13:29,679 --> 00:13:31,000
But don't criticize Yani.

315
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,120
Our family's problem

316
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:32,919
is my own to bear.

317
00:13:32,919 --> 00:13:33,799
It has nothing to do with her.

318
00:13:34,039 --> 00:13:34,720
Qingzhi.

319
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,200
Ignore what your brother said.

320
00:13:36,679 --> 00:13:37,960
Yani is a good lady.

321
00:13:38,279 --> 00:13:39,600
Don't let this matter

322
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,919
come between you two.

323
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,960
We'll pack our things later

324
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:43,840
and move out tomorrow.

325
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:44,240
Okay?

326
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:47,759
Sigh.

327
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:48,799
Goodness.

328
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,080
If I had known how difficult it is

329
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:51,000
to live in the city,

330
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:53,000
I would've urged you to go back.

331
00:13:53,919 --> 00:13:54,399
Dad.

332
00:13:54,559 --> 00:13:55,759
We have already signed the lease

333
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:57,759
for that house.

334
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,639
We also paid half a year's rent.

335
00:13:59,679 --> 00:14:00,480
We can't cancel it.

336
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:04,159
What do you think, Qingzhi?

337
00:14:05,559 --> 00:14:06,000
I

338
00:14:06,279 --> 00:14:08,159
respect Qinglai and Xingfu's decision.

339
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:10,720
You two decide.

340
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:11,519
It's fine with me.

341
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,919
I'd love to go back.

342
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:25,039
But right now,

343
00:14:25,639 --> 00:14:27,279
I already have a job.

344
00:14:28,159 --> 00:14:29,559
Everyone treats me well.

345
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,320
Besides,

346
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,879
I'll be a permanent employee in a month.

347
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:36,120
It'll be a shame to go back now.

348
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:39,080
Why not...

349
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,200
I think we will go back

350
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,279
sooner or later.

351
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,039
Our roots are there.

352
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,519
Yes.

353
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,679
I'd like to stay in the city

354
00:14:48,679 --> 00:14:49,799
and learn more.

355
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:50,679
Do what I can now

356
00:14:50,679 --> 00:14:51,440
and see more things.

357
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,480
Besides,

358
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:53,200
both of us

359
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,360
have stable jobs.

360
00:14:55,200 --> 00:14:56,000
Maybe a while longer.

361
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,080
We're only just starting out.

362
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,000
Mr. Wan said this.

363
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,080
If they prefer to stay in the city,

364
00:15:01,159 --> 00:15:02,559
they should stay.

365
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,799
You're free to come and go.

366
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:04,720
That's right.

367
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,600
It's just Little Dou.

368
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:08,559
Your dad and I will look after Little Dou.

369
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,399
Rest assured.

370
00:15:10,840 --> 00:15:11,759
Alright?

371
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:12,840
Okay.

372
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:13,600
Okay.

373
00:15:16,759 --> 00:15:17,639
Eat.

374
00:15:17,799 --> 00:15:19,000
Eat up. It's getting cold.

375
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,080
Eat.

376
00:15:37,639 --> 00:15:38,679
What's the matter?

377
00:15:41,679 --> 00:15:42,840
Skipped dinner again?

378
00:15:44,679 --> 00:15:46,039
Are you angry with me again?

379
00:15:47,879 --> 00:15:49,799
I'm not angry at you.

380
00:15:52,679 --> 00:15:53,279
Take a seat.

381
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,240
Mom.

382
00:16:02,519 --> 00:16:02,919
Yes.

383
00:16:05,039 --> 00:16:06,360
Can I ask you something?

384
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:08,000
What is it?

385
00:16:11,759 --> 00:16:12,720
Well,

386
00:16:13,240 --> 00:16:14,720
you had all the goods back then.

387
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,360
Why did you end up choosing Dad?

388
00:16:18,519 --> 00:16:19,519
Didn't your mom oppose it?

389
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:23,580
I

390
00:16:24,750 --> 00:16:26,270
was indeed the creme of the crop.

391
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:28,030
And I was a beauty.

392
00:16:29,060 --> 00:16:30,470
I had many suitors.

393
00:16:31,820 --> 00:16:32,470
My mom

394
00:16:32,470 --> 00:16:33,470
opposed it of course.

395
00:16:35,270 --> 00:16:36,030
However,

396
00:16:36,030 --> 00:16:36,820
I was

397
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:39,540
blinded by love.

398
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:45,110
Your affection for Qingzhi is real, isn't it?

399
00:16:46,990 --> 00:16:47,990
After you get married,

400
00:16:47,990 --> 00:16:49,150
you'll understand.

401
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:51,060
Affection

402
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:51,940
and love.

403
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:54,420
Those things can't replace real life.

404
00:16:55,060 --> 00:16:55,870
All the good and bad.

405
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:57,750
But I think

406
00:16:57,870 --> 00:16:59,870
although you always bicker with my dad,

407
00:17:00,510 --> 00:17:02,110
you two are still in love with each other.

408
00:17:02,110 --> 00:17:03,230
You seem happy.

409
00:17:05,300 --> 00:17:05,990
That's true.

410
00:17:07,430 --> 00:17:09,190
Your dad is quite good.

411
00:17:10,670 --> 00:17:11,620
And he cooks well.

412
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:14,580
Sometimes,

413
00:17:14,580 --> 00:17:16,300
I tend to be a little willful,

414
00:17:16,430 --> 00:17:16,990
aren't I?

415
00:17:17,300 --> 00:17:18,860
A little?

416
00:17:19,670 --> 00:17:21,470
You have the worst temper.

417
00:17:24,190 --> 00:17:24,710
Gosh.

418
00:17:25,990 --> 00:17:26,950
But still,

419
00:17:29,230 --> 00:17:30,230
I feel like I need to tell you.

420
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:31,820
It's not

421
00:17:31,820 --> 00:17:32,820
that Qingzhi is not good.

422
00:17:33,340 --> 00:17:34,300
I think Qingzhi

423
00:17:34,950 --> 00:17:35,750
is practical.

424
00:17:36,300 --> 00:17:37,340
And

425
00:17:38,270 --> 00:17:39,510
he has the drive.

426
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:41,820
But if you marry him,

427
00:17:42,380 --> 00:17:43,820
you're not marrying only him.

428
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:47,580
You're marrying into his whole family.

429
00:17:48,430 --> 00:17:50,190
My situation is different from yours.

430
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:52,230
The gap between urban and rural areas

431
00:17:52,230 --> 00:17:53,710
isn't as big as before.

432
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:57,030
Today, I got so upset

433
00:17:57,100 --> 00:17:59,190
not because Qingzhi's parents came.

434
00:17:59,990 --> 00:18:02,380
It's because he wasn't being honest with me.

435
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:05,990
Mom.

436
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:10,430
What's the matter, Mom?

437
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:12,580
Don't cry.

438
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:14,140
Trust me.

439
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:15,380
I will be happy.

440
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:18,430
I really want you to be happy.

441
00:18:19,540 --> 00:18:21,190
You are my heart and soul.

442
00:18:21,780 --> 00:18:22,430
You know that?

443
00:18:25,060 --> 00:18:26,270
Alright, I know.

444
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:28,860
I have you.

445
00:18:30,620 --> 00:18:32,510
I feel so blessed because I have you.

446
00:18:33,580 --> 00:18:34,540
I know.

447
00:18:39,710 --> 00:18:40,140
Mom.

448
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,270
Leave them here.

449
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:43,230
I'll do the dishes.

450
00:18:43,710 --> 00:18:44,430
Leave it.

451
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:49,060
Qinglai.

452
00:18:55,100 --> 00:18:55,780
I know

453
00:18:56,230 --> 00:18:57,190
you're upset

454
00:18:57,190 --> 00:18:58,670
about the current living arrangement.

455
00:19:00,860 --> 00:19:02,860
I mentioned it to Qingzhi just now.

456
00:19:03,030 --> 00:19:04,580
He's not an unreasonable person.

457
00:19:04,950 --> 00:19:06,860
It's just that Yani is also in the equation.

458
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:09,820
If you ruin

459
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:12,030
Qingzhi's relationship because of this matter,

460
00:19:12,300 --> 00:19:13,230
as his older brother,

461
00:19:13,230 --> 00:19:14,100
won't you feel regretful?

462
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:15,580
Besides, Yani's father

463
00:19:15,580 --> 00:19:16,620
got you your job,

464
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:17,860
right?

465
00:19:18,990 --> 00:19:20,270
If because of this,

466
00:19:20,750 --> 00:19:21,780
he loses his family,

467
00:19:21,780 --> 00:19:23,140
that would be a shame.

468
00:19:25,710 --> 00:19:26,470
Qinglai.

469
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:28,060
Listen to me.

470
00:19:28,780 --> 00:19:29,620
Move out, okay?

471
00:19:32,910 --> 00:19:33,510
Mom.

472
00:19:34,820 --> 00:19:35,950
I didn't say I won't move out.

473
00:19:38,540 --> 00:19:39,140
Alright.

474
00:19:39,340 --> 00:19:40,430
It's all good.

475
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:48,910
Little Dou.

476
00:19:49,430 --> 00:19:50,300
It's Mommy.

477
00:19:52,750 --> 00:19:54,540
How I wish to be with you every day.

478
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:57,670
But if I

479
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:59,190
go back like this,

480
00:20:00,060 --> 00:20:01,340
I will feel bad.

481
00:20:05,670 --> 00:20:07,540
Since I've been in the city,

482
00:20:07,780 --> 00:20:09,100
I've met a lot of people

483
00:20:10,470 --> 00:20:11,780
and experienced a lot.

484
00:20:13,820 --> 00:20:15,060
It's not easy.

485
00:20:15,060 --> 00:20:15,910
But right now,

486
00:20:15,910 --> 00:20:17,230
I finally see the light.

487
00:20:18,910 --> 00:20:19,780
I hope

488
00:20:19,780 --> 00:20:20,540
you can be

489
00:20:21,230 --> 00:20:22,670
like the kids in the city.

490
00:20:24,030 --> 00:20:25,030
Get an education.

491
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:26,430
Widen your horizons.

492
00:20:27,340 --> 00:20:28,580
This way, you'll have more opportunities

493
00:20:28,580 --> 00:20:29,670
in the future.

494
00:20:33,750 --> 00:20:35,060
You'll have a better life

495
00:20:35,100 --> 00:20:36,100
than me.

496
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:38,340
Don't you agree?

497
00:20:40,060 --> 00:20:41,580
Please wait a bit longer for me.

498
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:49,470
I will do my best.

499
00:20:49,710 --> 00:20:50,820
I'll live with gusto.

500
00:21:52,470 --> 00:21:53,100
What is it?

501
00:21:53,820 --> 00:21:54,470
Yani.

502
00:21:56,060 --> 00:21:57,340
Qinglai and Xingfu

503
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:58,510
have found a place.

504
00:21:59,030 --> 00:22:00,100
They're moving out tomorrow.

505
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:01,780
My parents

506
00:22:01,780 --> 00:22:03,190
are also going back tomorrow.

507
00:22:04,820 --> 00:22:05,820
Yani, I'm sorry.

508
00:22:06,380 --> 00:22:07,030
I shouldn't have

509
00:22:07,030 --> 00:22:08,140
kept this from you.

510
00:22:10,270 --> 00:22:11,540
Can you not lie to me

511
00:22:11,540 --> 00:22:12,670
again?

512
00:22:13,100 --> 00:22:14,100
Why can't you

513
00:22:14,100 --> 00:22:15,340
just talk to me?

514
00:22:16,100 --> 00:22:16,710
Yani.

515
00:22:16,820 --> 00:22:18,340
I promise there won't be a next time.

516
00:22:18,990 --> 00:22:20,190
Please give me one more chance.

517
00:22:23,140 --> 00:22:23,990
There you go again.

518
00:22:25,300 --> 00:22:26,300
The same old trick.

519
00:22:27,230 --> 00:22:28,230
I'm going to bed.

520
00:22:49,230 --> 00:22:50,710
What are you doing here?

521
00:22:51,190 --> 00:22:52,430
Am I not allowed to be here?

522
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:55,470
Have your parents left?

523
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:56,710
Yes.

524
00:22:56,990 --> 00:22:58,270
They left in the morning.

525
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:02,380
Put the things in the car.

526
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:07,300
Go on.

527
00:23:10,990 --> 00:23:11,540
Xingfu.

528
00:23:11,910 --> 00:23:12,430
Qinglai.

529
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:13,300
Qinglai, this way.

530
00:23:13,710 --> 00:23:14,470
Yani.

531
00:23:14,950 --> 00:23:15,780
Why are you here?

532
00:23:16,380 --> 00:23:17,990
Qingzhi said you broke up with him.

533
00:23:17,990 --> 00:23:19,270
It was like he had lost his soul.

534
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:21,300
I'm not here for him.

535
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:22,780
I'm here for you.

536
00:23:23,230 --> 00:23:24,030
I come to see

537
00:23:24,030 --> 00:23:24,860
if there's anything I could help with.

538
00:23:25,670 --> 00:23:26,820
So you two made up?

539
00:23:28,580 --> 00:23:29,580
I guess.

540
00:23:30,270 --> 00:23:31,190
That's good.

541
00:23:31,380 --> 00:23:32,380
-I'll take that.
-That's good.

542
00:23:33,580 --> 00:23:34,540
Let me tag along.

543
00:23:44,510 --> 00:23:45,910
You guys go ahead and settle in.

544
00:23:46,140 --> 00:23:46,540
Okay.

545
00:23:46,540 --> 00:23:47,230
Sure.

546
00:23:47,340 --> 00:23:48,620
Here's the key.

547
00:23:49,060 --> 00:23:50,060
Call me if there is anything.

548
00:23:50,230 --> 00:23:50,910
Sure thing.

549
00:23:51,190 --> 00:23:51,780
Thank you.

550
00:23:51,780 --> 00:23:52,430
No worries.

551
00:23:54,750 --> 00:23:55,620
Qingzhi.

552
00:23:56,230 --> 00:23:57,230
How could you let them

553
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:58,380
stay in such a place?

554
00:24:01,230 --> 00:24:01,910
Xingfu.

555
00:24:01,990 --> 00:24:02,430
Yes?

556
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:04,190
Why don't

557
00:24:04,300 --> 00:24:05,540
you move back to our house?

558
00:24:05,710 --> 00:24:06,270
Yes.

559
00:24:06,750 --> 00:24:07,750
That won't do.

560
00:24:08,140 --> 00:24:09,030
We can't keep

561
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:09,860
living there.

562
00:24:10,910 --> 00:24:12,060
This place isn't bad.

563
00:24:12,140 --> 00:24:13,300
It will look different

564
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:14,510
once everything is tidy.

565
00:24:14,910 --> 00:24:16,190
Thank you for bringing us here.

566
00:24:16,190 --> 00:24:16,950
You guys should go.

567
00:24:17,140 --> 00:24:17,860
Why don't we help

568
00:24:17,860 --> 00:24:18,540
to tidy up?

569
00:24:18,670 --> 00:24:18,950
Yes.

570
00:24:18,950 --> 00:24:19,780
It's okay, really.

571
00:24:19,910 --> 00:24:21,860
This place is only so big.

572
00:24:21,910 --> 00:24:23,270
It'll take only a minute to clean up.

573
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:25,100
You two should go home.

574
00:24:25,990 --> 00:24:27,190
Xingfu, what else do you need?

575
00:24:27,190 --> 00:24:28,030
We'll buy it for you.

576
00:24:28,580 --> 00:24:29,580
Need you to ask?

577
00:24:29,910 --> 00:24:30,750
We'll just go first.

578
00:24:30,820 --> 00:24:31,430
Go.

579
00:24:36,030 --> 00:24:37,060
What's with you?

580
00:24:37,710 --> 00:24:38,950
Yani is already being very nice,

581
00:24:38,950 --> 00:24:39,820
going out of her way.

582
00:24:39,910 --> 00:24:40,990
Look at that face of yours.

583
00:24:41,030 --> 00:24:42,510
You're pulling a long face.

584
00:24:42,910 --> 00:24:44,270
I'm not upset with Yani.

585
00:24:44,340 --> 00:24:45,470
I'm upset with Qingzhi.

