919
00:38:27,910 --> 00:38:29,220
You even learned a lot?

920
00:38:30,780 --> 00:38:31,780
That's amazing.

921
00:38:33,990 --> 00:38:35,100
Is the person your mentor?

922
00:38:38,100 --> 00:38:39,140
You could say that.

923
00:38:41,140 --> 00:38:42,070
This person is

924
00:38:42,510 --> 00:38:43,350
very brave,

925
00:38:43,870 --> 00:38:44,550
strong-willed,

926
00:38:44,830 --> 00:38:45,510
studious,

927
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:46,660
